outputMog_mdl.GROUP_VARIABLES:
GRPVc = POP_Vc*(WT/70)
GRPVp = POP_Vp
GRPCL = POP_CL
GRPka = POP_ka
GRPQ = POP_Q
GRPMTT = POP_MTT
GRPn = POP_n
outputMog_mdl.INDIVIDUAL_VARIABLES:
Vc = GRPVc*exp(eta_PPV_Vc)
        Vp = GRPVp*exp(eta_PPV_Vp)
        CL = GRPCL*exp(eta_PPV_CL)
        ka = GRPka
        Q = GRPQ
        MTT = GRPMTT
        n = GRPn
        kcp = Q/Vc
        kpc = Q/Vp
        kel = CL/Vc
        ktr = (n+1)/MTT
        LNFAC = ln(2.5066)+(n+0.5)*ln(n)-n
        F1 = 0
        if (AMT>0) {
	PODO = AMT
}
outputMog_mdl.ESTIMATION:
IPRED = CENTRAL/Vc
if (IPRED==0) {
	IPRED = 0.0001
}
W = RUV_PROP*IPRED
IRES = DV-IPRED
IWRES = IRES/W
Y = IPRED+W*eps_RUV_EPS
